Feature: Hotel room booking in adactin application

Scenario: Login page
Given user is able to launch the URL
When user is able to give username
And user is able to give password
Then user is able to login if username and password are correct

Scenario: Search page
Given user selects the location
When user selects the hotel
And user selects the room
And user selects the room type
And user gives check in date
And user gives check out date
And user selects the adults 
And user selects the child
And user clicks the search
And user gives the select hotel
Then user gives the continue 

Scenario: Book hotel
Given user enters first name
And user enters last name
And user enters address
And user enters card no
And user verify the card type 
And user verify the  month
And user verify the year
And user enters the cvv
And user clicks the book button
Then user clicks the logout button